  "notes": "Arc Testnet v1 privacy ship — mirrors Fuji shape but uses real Circle EURC as collateral leg (Arc's M1/M2 markets pair USDC<->real EURC, not MockEURC). Self-deployed Morpho Blue at 0x3c9b... (Arc has no canonical Morpho). UUPS proxy ASP_POSTMAN role currently held by deployer; rotate to relayer EOA after the relayer service has a stable key. 2026-05-23 basket expansion: MXNB / QCAD / cirBTC / AUDF pools deployed in 100%-hot mode via AddArcBasketPrivacyPools.s.sol — `hotReservePct = 10000` so `_rebalance` early-returns and the Morpho rehyp path is never touched (canonical Arc Morpho markets are USDC-loan, not basket-asset-loan, so registry.paramsOf would have reverted). USDC is passed as a dummy collateral constructor arg purely to satisfy the non-zero / != asset checks; it is never read at runtime."
